(6, 'ITIL 4 Foundation', '2021-05-29 19:54:51', '2021-05-29 19:54:51', '3 Years', 1, 1, 'fb549482ed1cc0454b6ba457f67e783d.png', '<p>Based on Best Practices in IT Service Management - ITIL&reg;&nbsp;4 Foundation Certification is a globally recognized examination-based professional credential program that is accredited and managed by PEOPLECERT &ndash; the leading Player in Global Certifications Industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ITIL&reg;&nbsp;4 Foundation Certification has been specifically designed for IT Project Infrastructure Staff working across industry verticals like IT/ITeS, Software, Construction, Power/Energy, Government, Defense, Telecom, Manufacturing, Research &amp; Development, Product Development, Oil &amp; Gas, to name a few.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This certification serves as a foundation to build a career in the IT Infrastructure/IT Service Support Role.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top companies recommend their IT, Networking, Desktop Support, IT Infrastructure Support, Database Support, Application Support to become ITIL&reg;&nbsp;Certified as they know that have an idea of what to expect from an ITIL&reg;&nbsp;Certification Holder, as opposed to someone else with the same Degree/Diploma but no ITIL&reg;&nbsp;Certification.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With an overall experience of delivering 300+ ITIL&reg;&nbsp;4 Foundation Certification to 5,000+ participants, KnowledgeWoods has emerged as a Trusted Partner for the ITIL&reg;&nbsp;4 Foundation Certification Initiative.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We understand what ITIL&reg;&nbsp;Certification means to you, and as such, provide you multiple training modes like Classroom, LIVE Learning &amp; e-Learning to prepare for ITIL&reg;&nbsp;Certification and Prepare for a career in IT Infrastructure Services role.</p>', '<p>ITIL Simulation Test</p>', '<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>\r\n			<p><strong>Module No.</strong></p>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th>Module Name</th>\r\n			<th>Topics Covered</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Module I</strong></p>