(267, 1, 1, 1, 'A new law is expected within the next four-to-five months that will affect the business type of products. The next product launch is starting and should be completed within three months. Unfortunately, the new product would not meet the requirements of the proposed law.\n  \n How should the project manager respond to this potential problem?', 1, 1, 'High Complex', 'This new law can have a profound effect on the project. It will certainly lead to new potential risks, new assumptions and a possible charter change.\n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018), 4. Project Integration Management / 4.1.3 Develop Project Charter: Outputs, p81', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
