(996, 1, 3, 1, 'You are nearing the end of your project when additional requirements were demanded by a group of stakeholders. This has become a problem for you because you have not taken the time or cost into account in the project plan to perform these requirements. What is the best thing you can do to prevent such a problem in future?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'Key sentence here is \"group of stakeholders\". So this group of stakeholders were not taken into confidence and engaged properly. Hence you would need to pay more attention to stakeholder management going forward', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
