(1063, 1, 3, 1, 'Identify where Comparing actual to baseline schedules, examining the statement of work, understanding cost overruns, and assessing risk occur?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'Examining SoW, understanding cost over runs, & assessing risks are key actions here. These are performed during audits. These actions are not done during any of the other options', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
