(1065, 1, 3, 1, 'You are a project manager of BlindTrust Medical Technologies. You are experiencing lot of cases of scope creep in your project due to which your project seems to become never ending. For this purpose, all of the following scope management process can be utilized EXCEPT?', 1, 1, 'Medium', 'The question is to identify a non PM process & \"Scope Reporting\" is not a PM process in scope management process.', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
