(1068, 1, 3, 1, 'You are currently working as a project manager on a major telecom infrastructure project. Your project sponsor has asked you for changes to be implemented in current scope of project. What should you do?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'First thing you do when a CR is raised (even requested by the Sponsor or customer) is to analyze the impact & report the potential impact to the change requestor', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
