(1114, 1, 3, 1, 'Michael has just joined ABC Enterprises. He finds that his role in organization is to keep track of status and make some of the minor decisions on the project without having to run them by the functional manager. He is working as:', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'Michael does not have full authority over the project & his primary role is to track the project progress', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(1115, 2, 6, 1, 'Michael has just joined ABC Enterprises. He finds that his role in organization is to keep track of status and make some of the minor decisions on the project without having to run them by the functional manager. He is working as:', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'Michael does not have full authority over the project & his primary role is to track the project progress', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(1116, 1, 2, 1, 'You have recently joined ABC Enterprises as Project Manager. You find that the team members report both to you and the functional head. But you have more authority then functional head. Which type of organization structure you are working in?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'You have slightly more authority over the Functional Head (Department Head), hence it is a strong matrix where a PM belonging to Projects Department is managing the project', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(1117, 2, 6, 1, 'You have recently joined ABC Enterprises as Project Manager. You find that the team members report both to you and the functional head. But you have more authority then functional head. Which type of organization structure you are working in?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'You have slightly more authority over the Functional Head (Department Head), hence it is a strong matrix where a PM belonging to Projects Department is managing the project', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(1118, 1, 3, 1, 'Thomas is a project manager working on a construction project near New York City. He is currently sequencing the activity list. Which Process Group is he currently working on?', 1, 1, 'Medium', 'Activities are sequenced in Planning & re-sequenced if required in \"Monitoring & Controlling\". M&C is not given as an option, hence Planning is the right answer', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
