(1120, 1, 3, 1, 'Thomas is a project manager working on a construction project near New York City. He is currently Sequencing the activity list. Which Knowledge Area is he currently working on?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'Activities are created & sequenced in Schedule Management KA', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
