(1124, 1, 3, 1, 'Jessie has just started working on a new IT project that has zero float. He is working in Strong Matrix Organization. Which of the below statement is TRUE?', 1, 1, 'Medium', 'In Strong Matrix (All Matrix & Functional) organizations the project team always has a home. \n \n All other statements are false', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
