(1181, 1, 2, 1, 'Carrie is a project manager. Two of her team members are engaged in a conflict and they reach out to her for a solution. However, one team member wants them to resolve the conflict on their own. Which conflict resolution Technique did she use?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'When one stakeholder wants to resolve the confict any of the techniques can be used. In the current scenario all the others barring Withdrawal need both stakeholders to be engaged. Hence most logical choice is Withdrawal.\n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018) 9. Project Resource Management / 9.5.2.1 Interpersonal and Team Skills, p348', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
