(1184, 1, 1, 1, 'Project A has a NPV of $1 million and IRR of 4%. Project B hand a NPV of $1.1 million and IRR of $3.9%. Which project should you select?', 1, 1, 'High Complex', 'Since the IRR are almost similar one should choose the project with greater NPV. Best choice in this situation will be Project B.', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
