(1187, 1, 3, 1, 'Kirti works for a non-profit organization. On one of her projects, a customer wants her to use the schedule compression technique, so that they can complete the work ahead of schedule. Which are the two schedule compression techniques that can be used and what is the difference between them?', 1, 1, 'Medium', 'To execute the project quickly, Kirti needs to fast track and Crash which combines is called schedule compression. In Crashing, you add more resources and in Fast Tracking, you do things in parallel.\n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018) PMI/PMI/6.5.2.6/253', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
