(1222, 1, 2, 1, 'Sam is working on implementing a security solution for a customer. One of the tasks to be accomplished for a smooth project execution is to identify all the stakeholders involved. And for any complex project, such as this, once the project stakeholders are identified, the next step is to classify these stakeholders based on their current and desired engagement levels. What is the benefit of classifying the project stakeholders?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'Once the stakeholders are classified it becomes easy for project manager to stategise and handle requirements of each project stakeholders differently. Best choice in current scenario is option A.\n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018), Part 2 The Standard for Project Management / 13.1 Identify Stakeholders , pp 549-550', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
