(1256, 1, 3, 1, 'Joe is a new PM who needs to procure a software from a vendor. He decides to put in a purchase order for the software. However, after speaking to his peers, he is doubtful that this is the correct way to go about it. Which of the following is the most appropriate way to go about purchasing the software?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'PM needs to follow the process and never understimate the kind of procurement. Usage of procured product and services may have legal implications and hence needs to be vetted and should follow complete contracting procedure. The best choice for Joe is D.', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
