(1261, 1, 2, 1, 'Brian is the project manager of a global project located across the world. Due to the nature of the project, a lot of the communication happens virtually across multiple time zones. As the project is progressing, Brian notices that there has been a gradual deterioration in the quality of communication between the team members. What is the called?', 1, 1, 'High Complex', 'Transmit message. The message is sent via a communication channel. The transmission of this message may be compromised by various physical factors such as unfamiliar technology or inadequate infrastructure. Noise and other factors may be present and contribute to loss of information in transmission and/or reception\n of the message.\n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018), 10. Project Communications Management / 10.1.2.4 COMMUNICATION MODELS/ p408', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
