(1305, 1, 3, 1, 'Your company receives a new contract. It\'s your responsibility to look at different vendors on one of the modules of the project. However, you will make this decision once you actively start working on the project. To be prepared, you plan on increasing the existing list of sellers. Which technique can you use?', 1, 1, 'High Complex', 'Advertising is communicating with users or potential users of a product, service, or result. Existing lists of potential sellers often can be expanded by placing advertisements in general circulation publications such as selected newspapers or in specialty trade publications. Most government jurisdictions require public advertising or online posting of pending government contracts.\n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018), 12. Project Procurement management /12.2.2.2 ADVERTISING, p534', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
