(1356, 1, 3, 1, 'You are working on a project where one of the components require you to outsource the work. So you conduct a bidder conference where you invite all the vendors in one room to ask questions. As a result of the bidder conference, all the sellers submit their bids. What should you do next?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'Once the bidder conference is done and proposals have come from Bidders, as a process, we will have to select the Seller. In the current situation best choice is A.\n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018), 12. Project Procurement Management', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
