(1364, 1, 3, 1, 'You are managing a project that is running smoothly without risks or insues. Suddenly, you have been hit by an unknown risk and you have decided to stop work immediately. The contracted work has already begun and you are not sure how to handle this situation. What should you do next?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'Whenever the unknown risks hit the project, the best situation is to refer the contract documents to understand the impact of the unknowm risk and see the coverage the agreement provides due unknown risk. Best choice is A. \n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018), 11. Project Risk Management', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
