(1375, 1, 2, 1, 'Laurie is working as a project manager for a luxury sports car manufacturer. A key stakeholder reaches out to her asking for a budget related change. Laurie, without hearing much detail says \"No.\"What conflict resolution techniques Laurie using?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'Laurie is using the Withdrawal style which is Retreating from an actual or potential conflict situation; postponing the issue to be better prepared or to be resolved by others.\n  \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018), 9. Project Resource Management / 9.5.2.1 INTERPERSONAL AND TEAM SKILLS, p385', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
