(1378, 1, 3, 1, 'You are working to implement the WBS process for a new project in your organization. Prior to this project, nobody has formally used this process. One of your colleagues tells you that the lowest level of WBS is known as work package but they are not sure about the most detailed level of WBS. What is your response to them?', 1, 1, 'High Complex', 'By Defination: Work Package. The work defined at the lowest level of the work breakdown structure for which cost and duration are estimated and managed.\n  \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018), 5. Project scope management / 5.4.2.2 DECOMPOSITION, p195', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
