(1380, 1, 2, 1, 'Jason is working with a customer\'s core team to identify the stakeholders on the project. Prior to setting up a face to face session with the group, he develops a questionnaire and sends it out to the core team. He gives them a week to go through the questions and then they can continue the process. Which technique did Jason use?', 1, 1, 'High Complex', 'Brain writing. A refinement of brainstorming that allows individual participants time to consider the question(s) individually before the group creativity session is held. The information can be gathered in face-to-face groups or using virtual environments supported by technology.\n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018),13. Project Stakeholder Management / 13.1.2.2 DATA GATHERING, p548', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
