(1386, 1, 3, 1, 'You work for an organization that typically follows a functional organization. But, in this instance, you have been assigned as project manager. Your team shares many characteristics of a project team in a project-oriented organization. What kind of organization are we talking about?', 1, 1, 'Medium', 'The current situation is a combination of Functional and Projectised organisation. This the correct case of composite organisation. Best choice is D.', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
