(1392, 1, 2, 1, 'Neil has been assigned an extra-large project. Due to the nature of the project, Neil requested an additional PM who can help him on few of the modules within the project. His request was rejected due to shortage of resources. Neil started working on the charter with the help of project sponsor and documented it as a risk. The sponsor is fully aware of the risk, but approved the project charter anyway. What should Neil do next?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'In the intiation phase of the project after charter is prepared, PM needs to identify stakeholders irrespective on any kind of risks in the project.\n Best choice is D.', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
