(1548, 1, 2, 1, 'You are in the process of making sure team member conflicts are resolved amicably. You take strict actions as and when required. Which process are you currently in?', 1, 1, 'Medium', 'Manage Team is the process of tracking team member performance, providing feedback, resolving issues, and managing team changes to optimize project performance. The key benefit of this process is that it influences team behavior, manages conflict, and resolves issues. This process is performed throughout the project.\n \n Best choice is option C as PM is managing team based on current situation.\n \n PMBOK Guide Sixth Edition (2018) PMI/PMI/9.5 MANAGE TEAM/p382', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
