(1565, 1, 3, 1, 'You are a project manager for Community Trends, a nonprofit organization. Your project has come about because of a social need. Youre calculating performance measurements, and you know the following information: BAC = 900, ETC = 65, PV = 500, EV = 475, and AC = 425. Which of the following statements is true?', 1, 1, 'Complex', 'The SV for this project is 25, which means the project is behind schedule. The CV for this project is 50, which means the costs are lower than what you had planned for this point in time.', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
