(1572, 1, 2, 1, 'Within Agile, a T shaped person refers to what?', 1, 1, 'High Complex', 'Within Agile there is a concept that describes the degree to which individuals can take on work, according to their depth and breadth. T shaped people are considered generalizing specialists who have expertise in an area but can also contribute to other areas. I shaped people refers to those who have deep specialization in one domain and rarely contribute to work outside of that domain.', 0, 16, '1970-01-01 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL),
